  m_text: 'Strategic Notes & Tips:

    Elemental Counter: Pets with an elemental
    advantage will deal increased damage. Pay attention to matchups!


    Card Synergy:
    Different Cards possess unique abilities. Mix and match them wisely to fit your
    strategy.


    Capture Reward: Defeat the target Pet a required number of times
    to successfully conquer and unlock it. Train hard and collect them all!'
