  m_text: '"Pet Skills & Combat Cards

    Pet Skills: Each Pet may possess a unique
    special skill. Once the specific activation requirements are met during battle,
    tap the skill icon to unleash it!


    Battle Cards: Pay close attention to
    your inventory management:


    Attack Cards: Can be used repeatedly and will
    not be consumed after use.


    Other Cards (Support/Buff/Debuff): Are single-use
    only. They will disappear permanently from your inventory once activated, so
    use them wisely!"'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 669d4057d5f4e6d449b6b8b76b5a1c18, type: 2}
