  m_text: 'Step 1: From the Home screen, tap the Adventure button to start your journey.


    Step
    2: Select the Planet you wish to explore.


    Step 3: Choose the target Pet
    you want to conquer. Tapping it will take you to the Battle Preparation screen.


    Step
    4: Select one of your own Pets to deploy into battle.


    Step 5: Equip up
    to 5 Cards purchased from the Shop to gain a tactical advantage.


    Step 6:
    If you own a Guardian, select one that best matches your preferred playstyle.


    Step
    7: Tap the Start button to enter the battlefield!'
