      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '"Match-3 Board: Match 3 or more identical gems to trigger their powerful
    effects:


    Sword Gem: Unleashes an attack on the enemy.


    Heart Gem:
    Restores HP based on a percentage of your Pet''s maximum health.


    Mana Gem:
    Replenishes your Pet''s Mana.


    Shadow Gem: Randomly steals enemy stats and
    adds them to your own.


    Shield Gem: Creates a temporary shield that protects
    you for the next turn."'
